---
title: AI Chat Support - Sequence Diagram
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI as Chat UI
    participant GeminiAPI as Gemini AI
    participant BuildService

    User->>UI: Open AI chat
    UI->>UI: Initialize chat session
    UI->>User: Display chat interface
    
    loop Chat conversation
        User->>UI: Send message
        UI->>UI: Display user message
        UI->>GeminiAPI: sendMessage(message, context)
        
        alt Build-related question
            GeminiAPI->>BuildService: getCurrentBuildContext()
            BuildService->>GeminiAPI: Return build data
        end
        
        GeminiAPI->>GeminiAPI: Process message with AI
        GeminiAPI->>UI: Return AI response
        UI->>UI: Display AI message
        UI->>User: Show AI response
    end
    
    User->>UI: Close chat
    UI->>UI: Save chat history (optional)
